---
// VPN software recommendations for laptop users
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <BaseHead
    title="VPN Software for Laptops | LaptopVette"
    description="Safe VPN software recommendations for laptop users, protecting privacy and secure browsing on any network."
    path="/vpn-software"
    type="article"
  />
</head>
<body>
  <nav class="navbar">
    <div class="container nav-container">
      <a href="/" class="logo">Laptop<span>Vette</span></a>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <main class="article-container">
    <header class="article-header">
      <span class="category-tag">Privacy & Security</span>
      <h1>Best VPN Software for Laptops</h1>
      <p class="byline">Recommended VPN tools that help protect browsing and secure connectivity on any network.</p>
    </header>

    <section class="summary-section">
      <h2>Top VPN Picks</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>SafeVPN:</strong> Easy-to-use network security with minimal setup.</li>
        <li><strong>Secure Access VPN:</strong> Designed for remote work and safe public Wi-Fi access.</li>
        <li><strong>GuardianNet Lite:</strong> Low bandwidth usage, strong privacy protocols, and simple controls.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="detail-section">
      <h2>Why VPNs Matter for Laptops</h2>
      <p>VPN software encrypts internet traffic and helps protect laptops on unsecured networks, especially public Wi-Fi hotspots.</p>
      <p>These recommendations prioritize ease of use, minimal interference with common apps, and strong privacy protection.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="cta-section">
      <a href="/back-to-school-laptops" class="btn btn-primary">Return to Laptop Buying Guides</a>
    </section>
  </main>
</body>
</html>

<style>
  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  body { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; background: #f8fafc; color: #0f172a; line-height: 1.85; }
  .container { max-width: 1000px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 20px; }
  .navbar { background: #ffffff; border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0; padding: 20px 0; }
  .logo { font-size: 22px; font-weight: 700; text-decoration: none; color: #0f172a; }
  .logo span { color: #b91c1c; }
  .article-container { max-width: 1064px; margin: 50px auto; padding: 40px; background: #ffffff; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; border-radius: 12px; }
  .article-header { margin-bottom: 30px; }
  .category-tag { color: #b91c1c; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-size: 11px; }
  h1 { font-size: 34px; margin: 15px 0; line-height: 1.25; }
  .byline { color: #475569; font-size: 15px; margin-bottom: 25px; }
  h2 { margin: 64px 0 32px 0; font-size: 26px; color: #1e1b4b; font-weight: 700; border-left: 4px solid #b91c1c; padding-left: 15px; }
  h3 { font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700; color: #1e1b4b; margin: 32px 0 20px 0; line-height: 1.4; }
  .summary-section { margin-bottom: 40px; }
  .detail-section { margin-bottom: 40px; }
  .summary-section ul, .detail-section ul { margin: 24px 0 0 24px; color: #334155; padding: 0; }
  .summary-section li, .detail-section li { margin-bottom: 28px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 2.0; color: #334155; }
  .summary-section p, .detail-section p { margin-bottom: 1.8em; line-height: 2.0; text-align: justify; color: #334155; }
  .cta-section { margin-top: 56px; }
  .btn-primary { display: block; width: 100%; background: #b91c1c; color: #ffffff; padding: 14px 24px; border-radius: 8px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 700; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box; }
  .btn-primary:hover { background: #991b1b; }
</style>